{"tid":537461,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[中世紀大型MMO（Life Is Feudal）］港人分城公會招人","createTime":"2018-01-22T17:13:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T04:21:30.000Z","uid":11412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3a0b2e92589273abedbe3880f42d13140609b64d","tid":537461,"uid":11412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T17:13:33.000Z","msg":"《封建生活》是款大規模、以團體為重點的角色扮演遊戲，玩家將置身在如同現實般、非幻想風格的中世紀世界，在這個遊戲世界中有著危機潛伏，玩家需要團隊合作來蒐集資源、建立營地，打造需要的工具，在古老的遊戲世界中形成功能完整的封建社會。玩家在這個社會中將會有自己的地位，不管是農夫、騎士甚至是皇室等。<br />\n《封建生活》中，玩家一開始所扮演的是一個單純又沒有裝備的農民，玩家需要透過蒐集資源、覓食並生火來建立營地；不久之後，玩家將會與其他玩家進行社交活動，共同蒐集資源並建立家園，玩家共同分工合作，在遊戲中扮演各種角色，像是獵人、採集者、村莊的防衛者等，要共同面對其他匪徒的來襲。你可以成為一位出色領主，兇猛戰士，為自己既公會打拼。<br />\n<br />\n喺呢度嘅每一個角色都係同樣重要，所有嘅生產戰鬥都係一環扣一環，例如你要生產一把劍上前線殺敵，你要礦工掘礦，鐵匠打鐵，戰士有足夠訓練先拎到到相應武器上前線彼甲殺敵。<br />\n<br />\n現時我哋主工會為咗擴大版圖，開出一個分會，希望招攬你哋嘅加入，成為我哋嘅一員，我哋每一個職業都有數位老手，可以帶領你哋比其他工會以更快嘅速度升級對應職業技能。加上主城資源充足，加入分會可以同時享受主城資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以下為分會福利：<br />\n<br />\n比其他工會有至少六陪升級速度（最快八陪加power plus）<br />\n<br />\n有老手帶住新手有咩唔識直接問<br />\n<br />\n冇階級觀念要鏟地連會長都要一齊鏟地，絕對唔會有黑奴嘅出現<br />\n<br />\n最緊要嘅就係有馬騎（馬匹全伺服器短缺）<br />\n<br />\nEtc....<br />\n<br />\n仲有我哋呢個團隊係一個鍾意同人打交嘅工會唔怕悶，一同中國佬外國佬總之傾掂數一個字就係打。<br />\n<br />\n要注意我哋係美1  Buyan服 要購買遊戲嘅話就要係官網買。以下係官方網站網址：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lifeisfeudal.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flifeisfeudal.com%2F&d=Izm59kg6lzzydDMux2p497%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=5288ede5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lifeisfeudal.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n如果想玩加入我哋嘅話可以係下邊留言或者加入我哋嘅discord群組：<a href=\"https://discord.gg/dDnFQ4F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FdDnFQ4F&d=Izm59kg6lzzydDMux2p497%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=8c9f3a76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/dDnFQ4F</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遊戲截圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/87/0001513087.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2F2KU%2F87%2F0001513087.JPG&h=fc8ea8c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/290080/ss_200c0ff1879fd1215e99df26941359469457d0e7.1920x1080.jpg?t=1515697496\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.akamai.steamstatic.com%2Fsteam%2Fapps%2F290080%2Fss_200c0ff1879fd1215e99df26941359469457d0e7.1920x1080.jpg%3Ft%3D1515697496&h=988b8ad3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4cfbb05a607d84cdeb31f1bdac177b0a542f5c48","tid":537461,"uid":27890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T17:14:41.000Z","msg":"What is this?"},{"pid":"e89aaba6ea37bb0c0677818c070f306d2a220e7a","tid":537461,"uid":168205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cfbb05a607d84cdeb31f1bdac177b0a542f5c48","tid":537461,"uid":27890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T17:14:41.000Z","msg":"What is this?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T17:24:58.000Z","msg":"沙盒式mmo"},{"pid":"80e98b8f9b7f5663cfd59be0bcdeca441c874ba9","tid":537461,"uid":98449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e89aaba6ea37bb0c0677818c070f306d2a220e7a","tid":537461,"uid":168205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cfbb05a607d84cdeb31f1bdac177b0a542f5c48","tid":537461,"uid":27890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T17:14:41.000Z","msg":"What is this?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T17:24:58.000Z","msg":"沙盒式mmo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T17:31:52.000Z","msg":"可以自己起城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82deb9fe6c11670528f88b07439ceba53cb94754","tid":537461,"uid":130454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T19:31:53.000Z","msg":"另外個post？"},{"pid":"9e5fd49b2068c0da938fb5fb64f2c9cb66b43a86","tid":537461,"uid":11412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82deb9fe6c11670528f88b07439ceba53cb94754","tid":537461,"uid":130454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T19:31:53.000Z","msg":"另外個post？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T01:17:51.000Z","msg":"連登好似有幾個公會，我地呢邊係戰鬥農民，之前冇咩收人，我地公會科技算Server最前果堆，基本上係list入面有得起既建築物設施都已經有齊，主公會既人算係hardcore果堆，而且本身係Your own版已有經驗，所以比其他公會發展得快，但而家再起新城同埋要多d人幫手打杖同建城，所以我地都開始再招人"},{"pid":"278504868c86889aaa6fa6ef72005e035909d30b","tid":537461,"uid":98449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T01:28:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>另外個post？</blockquote>連登好似有幾個公會，我地呢邊係戰鬥農民，之前冇咩收人，我地公會科技算Server最前果堆，基本上係list入面有得起既建築物設施都已經有齊，主公會既人算係hardcore果堆，而且本身係Your own版已有經驗，所以比其他公會發展得快，但而家再起新城同埋要多d人幫手打杖同建城，所以我地都開始再招人</blockquote><br />\n大部分生產技能都已經發展好，所以新玩家唔會逼住瘋狂練工 可以無咁辛苦 enjoy下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nskill tree可以睇：<a href=\"https://lifeisfeudal.com/MMORPGs-LiF/Crafting-skills-in-new-MMO-Life-is-Feudal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flifeisfeudal.com%2FMMORPGs-LiF%2FCrafting-skills-in-new-MMO-Life-is-Feudal&d=Izm59kg6lzzydDMux2p497%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=6a15782b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lifeisfeudal.com/MMORPGs-LiF/Crafting-skills-in-new-MMO-Life-is-Feudal</a>"},{"pid":"a189a7256905d2fa5bfeeb70d57efe2420552f69","tid":537461,"uid":11412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T05:05:55.000Z","msg":"就算普通食物質素都有最少兩陪速練功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/23/130545_123e1b46d14e54780406d3e2c42b73ff.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3